"Weergave van het vervolgkeuzemenu e-mailcampagne in Odoo's E-mailmarketing "
"applicatie."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing.rst:341
msgid ""
"If the desired campaign isn't available in the initial drop-down menu, "
